<h1>Edit Topic</h1>

<div class="row">

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for topics:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Make sure the topic is appropriate.</li>
      <li>Never insult dogs.</li>
      <li>Smile when you type.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-8">
    <!-- Rendering a 'partial' allows us to execute view code from a 'partial'
     file to increase modularity and simplify view files. Here *local* variables
       (locals) are passed to '_form.html.erb' -->
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { topic: @topic } %>
  </div>

</div>
